Dear Sir/Madam,

This is a reminder regarding the covenant breach notified vide our letter dated {{notice_date}}.

Breach Details:
Covenant: {{covenant_name}}
Breach Date: {{detection_date}}
Cure Period: {{cure_period_days}} days
Cure Deadline: {{cure_deadline}}
Days Remaining: {{days_remaining}}

We note that the cure period is expiring soon. Please provide an update on the remediation measures being taken and confirm whether the breach will be cured by the deadline.

If you anticipate any difficulty in curing the breach within the stipulated time, please inform us immediately so that we may consider appropriate steps including seeking consent from debenture holders for extension of cure period.

Yours faithfully,
For Axis Trustee Services Limited

Authorized Signatory

Dear Sir/Madam,

With reference to our breach notice dated {{notice_date}} regarding {{covenant_name}}, we are pleased to confirm that based on the financial information provided for {{testing_period}}, the covenant breach has been CURED.

Details:
Covenant: {{covenant_name}}
Previous Value (Breach): {{previous_value}} {{unit}}
Current Value: {{current_value}} {{unit}}
Required Threshold: {{comparison_display}} {{threshold}} {{unit}}
Status: COMPLIANT

The breach has been cured within the cure period and no further action is required at this time.

We appreciate the Company's prompt attention to this matter and look forward to continued compliance with the Trust Deed covenants.

Yours faithfully,
For Axis Trustee Services Limited

Authorized Signatory
